	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Just an FYI, <a href="http://atariage.com/forums/topic/280856-robo-ninja-climb-atari-2600/" class="postlink">I ported Robo-Ninja Climb to the Atari 2600</a>. Part of the fun was attempting to directly use as much of the NES code as possible (since they are both 6502), merely replacing the rendering, controls, etc.  A good bit had to be rewritten for the Atari, but I was happily surprised with how much I was able to reuse.

		

